OL,3,CNew police powers to 'close the gap'
OL,4,Con violent attackers without terror
OL,5,Clinks
OL,7,FPolice and courts will be given new
OL,8,Fpowers to target suspects believed to
OL,9,Fbe planning mass killings, the home
OL,10,Fsecretary has announced.
OL,12,FYvette Cooper said the powerful new
OL,13,Ftools would ensure the planning of
OL,14,Fmass attacks was taken "as seriously
OL,15,Fas terrorism".
