OL,3,CNew police powers to 'close the gap'
OL,4,Con violent attackers without terror
OL,5,Clinks
OL,7,FThe new powers, including the ability
OL,8,Fto apprehend suspects before they
OL,9,Fcarry out attacks, aim to "close the
OL,10,Fgap" between terror suspects, who can
OL,11,Fbe jailed for life for planning
OL,12,Fattacks, and individuals not driven by
OL,13,Fa particular ideology.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
