OL,3,CNew police powers to 'close the gap'
OL,4,Con violent attackers without terror
OL,5,Clinks
OL,7,FMs Cooper told BBC Radio 4's State of
OL,8,FTerror series: "There is a gap in the
OL,9,Flaw around the planning of mass
OL,10,Fattacks that can be just as serious
OL,11,F(as terrorism) in their implications
OL,12,Ffor communities, their impact, the
OL,13,Fdevastation that they can cause and
OL,14,Fthe seriousness of the crime.
OL,16,F"We will tighten legislation so that
OL,17,Fthat is taken as seriously as
OL,18,Fterrorism."
