OL,4,Con violent attackers without terror
OL,5,Clinks
OL,7,FShe said legislation would be similar
OL,8,Fto that which allows police to arrest
OL,9,Fterror suspects for steps taken to
OL,10,Fprepare for an attack, such as
OL,11,Fresearch, which is not currently
OL,12,Favailable without links to an
OL,13,Fideological cause.
OL,15,F"We've seen cases of growing numbers
OL,16,Fof teenagers potentially radicalising
OL,17,Fthemselves online and seeing all kinds
OL,18,Fof extremist material online in their
OL,19,Fbedrooms," she said.
